   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>CHAPTER TWO THE LAW OF THE SPIRIT OF LIFE FREEING US FROM THE LAW OF SIN AND OF DEATH Scripture Reading: Rom 8:2-13 The law of the Spirit of life having freed us v. 2a: Life the eternal life of God.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>The Spirit the resurrected Christ who was transfigured as the Spirit.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>Law the natural capacity, which is the person of the pneumatic Christ Himself as the embodiment of the processed Triune God.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>Freeing us causing us to be released from bondage and to have freedom.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>The law of sin and of death v. 2b: Sin the sin in the sinful nature, which is the evil nature of Satan, causing us to have the ability to sin.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>Death coming from sin, causing us to have no ability to do good.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>Law the natural sinning capacity in the sinful nature, which is the person of Satan himself as evil itself.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>The processed Triune God making the three parts of our being life: The Spirit of Christ being the pneumatic Christ entering into our spirit and making our spirit life vv.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>9-10.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>The Spirit and our spirit mingled as one spirit, spreading into our mind to make our mind life v. 6b.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>The resurrecting and indwelling Spirit of God reaching our body, making our body life also v. 11.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>The cooperation we should render: Setting our mind on the spirit v. 6b.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>Walking according to the spirit only v. 4b.</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>Putting to death the practices of the body by the Spirit v. 13.</S>
   </TEXT>
